FBIS4-32868 "drlat104_m_94009" FBIS-LAT-94-104 Daily Report 27 May 1994 Brazil PDT Names Darcy Ribeiro as Brizola Running Mate PDT Names Darcy Ribeiro as Brizola Running Mate PY2805005994 Rio de Janeiro Rede Globo Television in Portuguese 2300 GMT 27 May 94 PY2805005994 Rio de Janeiro Rede Globo Television Portuguese BFN [Text] PDT [Democratic Labor Party] presidential candidate Leonel Brizola today met PDT national executive committee members at his residence in southern Rio de Janeiro. This afternoon the PDT announced that Senator Darcy Ribeiro will be Brizola's running mate on the PDT ticket.
